item.title: CVE-2018-5481|2024-08-05T05:40:49.842Z -- netapp -- oncommand%20unified%20manager%20for%207-mode%20%28core%20package%29
item.description: OnCommand Unified Manager for 7-Mode (core package) prior to 5.2.4 uses cookies that lack the secure attribute in certain circumstances making it vulnerable to impersonation via man-in-the-middle (MITM) attacks.
